00:01:00.470 --> 00:01:00.930 align:middle line:90%
>> FORD: Absolutely.

00:01:00.930 --> 00:01:02.888 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Well, let's
start out with that part

00:01:02.888 --> 00:01:05.740 align:middle line:84%
of the conversation because
that's not how you were

00:01:05.740 --> 00:01:06.820 align:middle line:90%
naturally wired.

00:01:06.820 --> 00:01:10.010 align:middle line:10%
>> FORD: No, it was pretty
unpredictable that I'd be

00:01:10.010 --> 00:01:13.630 align:middle line:10%
sitting here in this chair
today talking to you about this

00:01:13.630 --> 00:01:14.600 align:middle line:10%
