kissing, or being affectionate.

00:01:32.580 --> 00:01:35.400 align:middle line:84%
But when I got
married, what I quickly

00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:39.010 align:middle line:84%
discovered in sort of
a very shocking manner

00:01:39.010 --> 00:01:41.800 align:middle line:84%
was that I had no
partnership skills.

00:01:41.800 --> 00:01:45.510 align:middle line:84%
I was really, really
good at being the boss.

00:01:45.510 --> 00:01:47.440 align:middle line:84%
I was used to
running a business.

00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:50.470 align:middle line:84%
But I had no clue how
to be a good partner.

00:01:50.470 --> 00:01:53.140 align:middle line:10%
And I quickly
decided that I needed

00:01:53.140 --> 00:01:54.880 align:middle line:10%
to become a student
of love, that I

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:58.760 align:middle line:10%
had manifested this awesome
soulmate, this incredible guy.

00:01:58.760 --> 00:02:01.140 align:middle line:10%
He exceeded my expectations.

00:02:01.140 --> 00:02:03.500 align:middle line:90%
And I was blowing it.

00:02:03.500 --> 00:02:06.050 align:middle line:84%
