beginning of the story.

00:02:06.050 --> 00:02:09.039 align:middle line:84%
>> REGINA: Yes, and, you know,
we teach best what we need

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:09.820 align:middle line:90%
to learn.

00:02:09.820 --> 00:02:11.090 align:middle line:90%
I mean, that's--

00:02:11.090 --> 00:02:13.150 align:middle line:84%
>> FORD: You teach what
you need to learn most.

00:02:13.150 --> 00:02:17.530 align:middle line:84%
And still, 18 years later,
I have learned a lot

00:02:17.530 --> 00:02:24.030 align:middle line:84%
and I have a lot of tools and
tricks in my emotional toolkit.

00:02:24.030 --> 00:02:26.380 align:middle line:84%
